$subhead UnderBar $$
$mindex underbar$$
The UnderBar (x00332) 
does not display at all in the context below.
Note that the 
UnderParenthesis (x0FE36) 
does display and
stretches to fit what it is under.
The input
$codep
	<munder>
		<mrow> <mi>a</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>b</mi> </mrow>
		<mo> &#x00332; </mo>
	</munder>
	<mspace width="1em"/>
	<munder>
		<mrow> <mi>a</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>b</mi> </mrow>
		<mo> &#x0FE36; </mo>
	</munder>
$$
results in the following output
$latex \[ \mathml{
	<munder>
		<mrow> <mi>a</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>b</mi> </mrow>
		<mo> &#x00332; </mo>
	</munder>
	<mspace width="1em"/>
	<munder>
		<mrow> <mi>a</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>b</mi> </mrow>
		<mo> &#x0FE36; </mo>
	</munder>
} \] $$


